Package: slumdown
Type: Package
Title: A Hugo Theme for Blogdown
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Danielle Navarro
Maintainer: Danielle Navarro <d.navarro@unsw.edu.au>
Description: Provides a simple theme for writing a blog in blogdown. The 
slumdown package contains wrapper functions to install the slum theme for
Hugo, convenience functions for customising the blog from within R, and a
mechanism to generate ggplot2 plots that match the blog colour palette.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    blogdown,
    here,
    usethis
